{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Expel all US diplomatic and military personnel from the UK",
        "additional_details": "We believe that due to recent actions from the US, the UK should consider severing diplomatic and military relations with the United States. Many consider the US' presence in our military bases to be dangerous, contributing to the US\u2019 military actions against other sovereign countries, and benefiting from the service and accommodation provided by UK military bases.",
        "background": "We urge the UK Government to expel all US diplomatic personnel from all US diplomatic missions in the UK, alongside expelling US military personnel and aircraft from RAF and other UK military bases.",
